msgstr "Currently, the following two search techniques can be summarized:"

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:14 ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:18 30ec1848f10843069032f613cee540cd 90f1638312d74ce0b230c9d2acf82bf8
