msgstr "Search by Keywords"

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:15 ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:28 94eced0949d34770b402a150416c4a98 b82db3f2a76747099090fb351e3d4fab
msgid "排除某个关键词"
msgstr "Exclude a Keyword"

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:20 abbdac42f0204244a76aaea56826af2a
msgid "将问题中的关键词提取出来并搜索它们，此时搜索结果会得到最匹配的结果。"
msgstr "Extract the keywords from the question and search for them. The search results will then show the best-matching results."

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:23 40c7a428332746dca49c5b3439bc13d8
msgid "比如问题为：``ESP32 的 Bluetooth LE 吞吐量是多少？``"
msgstr "For example, if the question is: ``What is the Bluetooth LE throughput of ESP32?``"

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:25 31c0dc5214f44366889ccac751d7a4c9
msgid "此时搜索：``ESP32``、``BLE`` 和 ``吞吐量`` 等关键字为宜。"
msgstr "In this case, it is recommended to search for keywords such as ``ESP32``, ``BLE`` , and ``throughput``."

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:30 8c422d45c482450e843b6daba70757bc
msgid "在搜索内容中添加一个标识符 ``-``, 格式为： ``关键词  -排除关键词``。此时搜索结果不会出现有排除关键词的结果。"
msgstr "Add the identifier ``-`` to the search content in the following format: ``keyword -excluded_keyword``.  In this case, search results containing the excluded keyword will not appear."

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:32 eb568b86405c43dfbfb5b89a30360757
msgid "比如搜索：``ESP32 -ble``。任何搜索结果中有 ``ble`` 的结果将会被过滤。"
msgstr "For example, search for: ``ESP32 -ble``. Any search result containing ``ble`` will be filtered out."

#: ../../source/docs/hardware-related/question-search.rst:37 dc7b16b90826417fac0dae94bc8e6268
msgid "在掌握上述 ``搜索问题技巧`` 后，可以利用 ESP-FAQ 已经做好的分类来提取想搜索问题里的关键词并搜索。以下是此网站的框架："
msgstr "After mastering the above ``Tips for Searching Questions``,  you can use the existing categories in ESP-FAQ to extract keywords from the question you want to search for and then search them.  The following is the framework of this website:"

